{"title":"草坪","authors":["卢晓圣"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":8,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"草坪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卢晓圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨绿在青翠中云集，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡展示生机的朝气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点缀使城市开始不拥挤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"氧气把阳光的心意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收集后给每一个人传递。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露珠又把存在的理由演义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枯荣的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有什么秘密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯独是面对生命的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那份坚毅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暴的冰冷暑热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从不对外提"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个坎坷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也当成又一次学习"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也看不出小草有什么神奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许是让庸俗氛围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把视线遮蔽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草的地位一直很低"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但沉稳而扎实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝对有根基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要生命面对太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾顶天立地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外形的大小"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不一定代表亮丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永恒的深浅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见得生命的各类会剖析"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贵贱和血统未必有什么联系"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻易的否认根本就不必，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细想想不见得有谁能如你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没必要让暂时的失意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妨碍你与太阳月亮去游戏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者倾听小鸟在唱歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有岁里的自然变化把记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存进历史的种种故事里。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}